  "raw_html": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"get-rng-state\">\n<span id=\"api-paddle-get-rng-state\"></span>\n<h1>get_rng_state<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#get-rng-state\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\"></a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">paddle.</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">get_rng_state</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span>\n<em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">device</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span>\n<span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">list</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">paddle.base.libpaddle.GeneratorState</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span></span>\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/blob/release/3.3/python/paddle/framework/random.py#L72\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a>\n</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>Get all random states of random generators of specified device.</p>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">\n           Parameters\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\">\n<p><strong>device</strong> (<em>str</em>) – This parameter determines the specific running device. It can be <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">cpu</span></code>, <co